# Network Diagnostics

## Description
Diagnose network issues in Zoom calls and meetings.

## Purpose
Analyze network performance, packet loss, latency, and bandwidth issues.

## Usage
```
network_diagnostics [options]
```

## Features
- Network quality analysis
- Packet loss detection
- Latency measurements
- Bandwidth utilization

## Keywords
network, diagnostics, latency, bandwidth, packet, loss
